    "description": {
      "zh": "Gribnik 打造的祈祷文臂带，保护使用者免受一种特殊的蚊子亚种侵扰——这种蚊子只在诺文斯克地区有分布。早在契约战争时期，就有新闻报道称当地出现了所谓“危险环境作战特种蚊子”（俄语缩写“SBEU”），但所谓目击者提供的大量证据中只有一小部分能经得起科学验证。",
      "en": "A prayer armband made by Gribnik to protect the owner from a special mosquito subspecies, observed only in the Norvinsk region. Back during Contract Wars, the news posted articles on the Hazardous Environment Combat Special mosquito (abbreviated \"SBEU\" in Russian), but only a small fraction of the data provided had been scientifically verified."
    },
